This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the compression of light field images using sparse coding techniques. It may also belong to multimedia (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT) sub-categories as these fields are closely related to image and video compression. Additionally, it may belong to graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with the representation and manipulation of 3D data.
